{"id":203095,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/global-voices-世界-在twitter上为特洛伊．戴维斯抗争/","date":"2011-12-27T09:13:15Z","modified":"2011-12-27T09:13:15Z","title":"Global Voices | 世界: 在Twitter上为特洛伊．戴维斯抗争","content":"<p><p><em><strong>本文英文原文发表于2011.9.21</strong></em></p>\n<p>美国50个州中有36个州可以<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Capital_punishment_in_the_United_States\" href=\"https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Capital_punishment_in_the_United_States\">合法执行死刑</a>，而<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Troy_Davis_case\" href=\"https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Troy_Davis_case\">特洛伊．戴维斯</a>的案子则激起了废死人士的怒气。戴维斯在1989年因谋杀警官的罪名遭起诉且被判有罪，但该审判中并没有提出<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_18947596?nclick_check=1\" href=\"http://www.mercurynews.com/breaking-news/ci_18947596?nclick_check=1\">DNA证据</a>，只有证人的证词，而其中许多证人甚至撤回供诉。</p>\n<p>戴维斯被判处死刑，执行日期预定为2007年7月17日，经他的律师上诉，非政府组织和无数知名人士的请求、呼吁之下，才得以暂缓死刑。<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Troy_Davis_case#Trial_and_conviction\" href=\"https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/wiki/Troy_Davis_case#Trial_and_conviction\">他的死刑改期两次</a> ，且两次都获得缓期执行。接着在2010一次遭到驳回的联邦上诉中，他的死刑再次改期为2011年9月21日。</p>\n<p>除了<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/09/21/lawyers-file-appeal-to-stay-troy-davis-execution/\" href=\"http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/09/21/lawyers-file-appeal-to-stay-troy-davis-execution/\">戴维斯的律师团</a>和<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/amnesty\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/amnesty\">国际特赦组织</a>吁请延缓死刑外，甚至也激起了某些知名人士如<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/KimKardashian/status/116471609161826305\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/KimKardashian/status/116471609161826305\">金．卡黛珊</a>，和绕舌歌手<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/BigBoi/status/116630894311247872\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/BigBoi/status/116630894311247872\">博爷</a>在推特上向他们的粉丝呼吁恳求支持。</p>\n<div>\n<dl>\n<dt><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/?attachment_id=255783\"><img title=\"Rally for Troy Davis\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/403861980-224x300.jpg\" alt=\"https://twitpic.com/6og5wc\" width=\"224\" height=\"300\" /></a></dt>\n<dd>图片来源：BigBoi，Twipic</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>\n<p>随着时间分秒逼近执行死刑的当地时间晚上7点，世界各地的人们持续用如#<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23TroyDavis\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23TroyDavis\">特洛伊．戴维斯</a>(#TroyDavis)、#<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23toomuchdoubt\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23toomuchdoubt\">太多疑点</a>(#TooMuchDoubt)和#<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23thewholeworldiswatching\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23thewholeworldiswatching\">全世界都在看</a>(#thewholeworldiswatching)等主题标签争取暂缓死刑。</p>\n<p>来自英国的Rachel_McCormack在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/R_McCormack/status/116644354013134848\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/R_McCormack/status/116644354013134848\">推特上写道</a>： 乔治亚州，我在伦敦的美国大使馆外冷的要命的看着 #thewholeworldiswatching</p>\n<p>同样来自英国CatherineBee<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/catharinebee/status/116644723900424192\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/catharinebee/status/116644723900424192\">分享了她的想法</a>： 伏尔泰说：“宁愿饶了个有罪的也不要滥杀一个无辜的”#thewholeworldiswatching #TroyDavis</p>\n<p>LizLemonCologne表达了很可能是许多人的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/LizLemonCologne/status/116645168412758017\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/LizLemonCologne/status/116645168412758017\">观点</a>： 追踪#thewholeworldiswatching 这主题标签伤透了我的心 #TroyDavis</p>\n<p>monstris<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/monstris/status/116648593359765504\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/monstris/status/116648593359765504\">感叹道</a>： 看今日民主，现在看着民主为了#TroyDavis解体吧，而人们还纳闷为什么我离开美国…#thewholeworldiswatching</p>\n<p>来自希腊的helion<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/helion/status/116646196545716224\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/helion/status/116646196545716224\">说</a>： 一个理应为人权堡垒的西方民主国家，不应该夺走一个可能是无罪的公民的性命#thewholeworldiswatching</p>\n<p>最后，他们的推特文和大量非线上行动主义者成为号召反对处决一位可能是无辜的人的力量。刚过晚间7点几分钟，戴维斯准予缓刑的新闻在推特传开来。Colorlines<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Colorlines/status/116649533525602304\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/Colorlines/status/116649533525602304\">说道</a>： 令人震惊!@democracynow正报导实实在在、紧要关头的死刑暂缓! 直播频道：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://democracynow.org\" href=\"http://democracynow.org/\">http://democracynow.org</a> #troydavis</p>\n<p>来自英国的GrahamSimmons<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/GrahamSimmons/status/116649220433383425\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/GrahamSimmons/status/116649220433383425\">评论道</a>： 今晚是人类的胜利 #TroyDavis #thewholeworldiswatching #fb</p>\n<p>但在兴奋之余graceishuman -在@DemocracyNow内传递新闻的记者- 澄清并<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/graceishuman\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/graceishuman\">说明</a>了该消息： 美国最高法院暂缓了#troydavis的死刑，代表将会延迟执行(为了再审?)而不是暂缓执行(透过Democracy Now)。</p>\n<p>美国广播公司<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://abcnews.go.com/US/troy-davis-execution-incites-twitter-outrage-protests-worldwide/story?id=14571862\" href=\"http://abcnews.go.com/US/troy-davis-execution-incites-twitter-outrage-protests-worldwide/story?id=14571862\">证实</a>了这个消息，表示“最高法院可以在今晚的任何时间或在接下来七天内决定是否通过他的死刑”。</p>\n<p>译者：Eddy Kuo</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/jillian-york/\" title=\"文章导读 Jillian C. York\">Jillian C. York</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span><br />\n · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/09/21/world-twitter-rallies-for-troydavis/\" title=\"阅读原文  [en]\">阅读原文  [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/12/26/10233/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%3A+%E5%9C%A8Twitter%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%8A%EF%BC%8E%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%E6%96%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F&#038;desc=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%3A+%E5%9C%A8Twitter%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%8A%EF%BC%8E%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%E6%96%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F&#038;text=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%3A+%E5%9C%A8Twitter%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%8A%EF%BC%8E%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%E6%96%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F&#038;title=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%3A+%E5%9C%A8Twitter%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%8A%EF%BC%8E%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%E6%96%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F&#038;title=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%3A+%E5%9C%A8Twitter%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%8A%EF%BC%8E%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%E6%96%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F&#038;title=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%3A+%E5%9C%A8Twitter%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%8A%EF%BC%8E%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%E6%96%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\" title=\"delicious\"><span>delicious</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.instapaper.com/edit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F26%2F10233%2F&#038;title=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%3A+%E5%9C%A8Twitter%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%BA%E7%89%B9%E6%B4%9B%E4%BC%8A%EF%BC%8E%E6%88%B4%E7%BB%B4%E6%96%AF%E6%8A%97%E4%BA%89\" title=\"Instapaper\"><span>Instapaper</span></a></span>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1001,"categories":[1],"tags":[19252]}